WEBVTT

00:00:00.740 --> 00:00:03.170
If you put up with this
and help me just this once...

00:00:03.170 --> 00:00:04.610
I'd rather die.

00:00:05.510 --> 00:00:06.510
Choi Yu Na!

00:00:07.350 --> 00:00:08.950
I know you don't want to do this,

00:00:08.950 --> 00:00:10.920
but how can you ask me
to kill you instead?

00:00:11.080 --> 00:00:14.120
Not me.
I'm telling you to kill CEO Baek.

00:00:15.250 --> 00:00:17.090
What?

00:00:19.090 --> 00:00:21.490
You call him a friend,
but you're always kissing up to him.

00:00:23.130 --> 00:00:26.460
Because you're so pathetic,
I'm losing everything to Jin Ju.

00:00:27.430 --> 00:00:28.430
I...

00:00:29.970 --> 00:00:32.200
would rather die
than lose to her like this.

00:00:34.970 --> 00:00:36.570
So don't you dare lose either.

00:00:37.140 --> 00:00:39.640
If you can't take what you want,
kill to keep what you have.

00:00:40.080 --> 00:00:41.210
Don't you dare...

00:00:42.210 --> 00:00:44.480
drag me down with you
and make me suffer too!

00:00:52.390 --> 00:00:53.390
Goodness.

00:01:08.710 --> 00:01:11.040
Rather than using Choi Sam Sik,

00:01:11.480 --> 00:01:13.210
we should use Choi Yu Na.

00:01:13.880 --> 00:01:15.380
Yes, sir.
I'll make the arrangements.

00:01:33.400 --> 00:01:35.370
Your wife came to see you
this afternoon.

00:01:36.100 --> 00:01:37.900
She said you should know
Director Kim...

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:39.470
has been frequenting Ihwachae.

00:01:41.840 --> 00:01:43.240
Like I don't already know.

00:01:44.540 --> 00:01:45.680
Tell everyone to assemble.

00:01:47.880 --> 00:01:50.420
It's about time I sorted out
these family matters.

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:07.600
You must have had such a hard time
on your own.

00:02:10.870 --> 00:02:15.470
When they learn I'm the Adele heir,
they treat me differently.

00:02:16.910 --> 00:02:19.410
They get envious, jealous,
act awkward around me,

00:02:20.880 --> 00:02:21.910
or they try to get close to me.

00:02:23.480 --> 00:02:25.420
But then when they find out
about my mother,

00:02:26.120 --> 00:02:27.590
their expressions become the same.

00:02:29.790 --> 00:02:32.960
It's a strange look of relief,
as if to say, "That figures,"

00:02:34.230 --> 00:02:37.830
while they subtly look down on me
for being an illegitimate son.

00:02:40.670 --> 00:02:41.670
That's why...

00:02:42.530 --> 00:02:43.940
keeping my background to myself...

00:02:45.240 --> 00:02:46.500
has become a habit for me.

00:02:47.370 --> 00:02:48.570
That's a bad habit.

00:02:50.580 --> 00:02:51.980
Illegitimate? Seriously?

00:02:52.680 --> 00:02:55.550
You should've gotten that crazy idea
out of your head immediately.

00:02:56.550 --> 00:03:00.080
From now on, if you get bad ideas,
you come straight to me.

00:03:00.650 --> 00:03:05.220
I'll remind you
how precious and perfect you are.

00:03:09.560 --> 00:03:10.760
What if I can't run right over?

00:03:12.830 --> 00:03:13.830
Then...

00:03:15.700 --> 00:03:16.900
you can look at this watch...

00:03:18.900 --> 00:03:21.570
and just remember
that we're always together.

00:03:29.480 --> 00:03:30.480
And...

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:34.050
from now on,
don't avoid me like you did today.

00:03:34.920 --> 00:03:37.660
If your mother finds out,
let's convince her together.

00:03:38.360 --> 00:03:41.690
If we work together,
we might be able to find a way.

00:03:43.460 --> 00:03:46.530
You're right.
If we do this together...

00:03:49.770 --> 00:03:52.500
With you by my side,
I feel like I can do anything.

00:04:17.260 --> 00:04:18.960
Hey, Min Jun!

00:04:20.300 --> 00:04:21.300
Code red.

00:04:21.670 --> 00:04:24.240
What's wrong?
Don't tell me we got caught.

00:04:24.800 --> 00:04:25.800
Not yet, but you're about to be.

00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:28.610
My father called a family meeting.

00:04:29.810 --> 00:04:32.840
Look, no time for details.
We've got to get her out of here.

00:04:32.910 --> 00:04:33.910
Hurry.

00:04:36.550 --> 00:04:39.480
(Park Tae Ho)

00:04:42.090 --> 00:04:43.190
Come on.

00:04:50.560 --> 00:04:51.560
Hey.

00:04:51.760 --> 00:04:54.200
You actually want people to think
you held hands with a guy?

00:04:54.700 --> 00:04:57.470
Do you want the big reveal
to be your coming-out?

00:04:58.200 --> 00:05:03.070
The key is to play it cool
and leave naturally.

00:05:03.910 --> 00:05:05.010
Watch and learn.

00:05:05.610 --> 00:05:06.610
Hey.

00:05:09.950 --> 00:05:10.950
Later.

00:05:15.990 --> 00:05:16.990
Hey.

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:20.730
Get home safe.

00:05:21.360 --> 00:05:23.060
Okay, I'm off. See you tomorrow.

00:06:04.940 --> 00:06:08.310
Why the sudden family meeting?
I have a bad feeling about this.

00:06:09.070 --> 00:06:10.140
Could he...

00:06:10.780 --> 00:06:13.510
have found out about Min Jun's plan
to study abroad?

00:06:24.960 --> 00:06:28.930
You ignore me at the office,
but now you want a family meeting?

00:06:31.430 --> 00:06:33.770
Did Manager Kang tell you
what I said?

00:06:37.340 --> 00:06:38.500
I knew it.

00:06:41.510 --> 00:06:44.910
Good. Then make it clear to them,
right here and now.

00:06:45.180 --> 00:06:47.780
Show them what it means to cross you
and step out of line.

00:06:50.050 --> 00:06:51.080
Listen up.

00:06:52.580 --> 00:06:54.520
Once the boys graduate from college,

00:06:54.920 --> 00:06:58.220
I'm giving them each an equal share
of Adele stock.

00:06:59.260 --> 00:07:00.260
Stock?

00:07:01.190 --> 00:07:03.530
This was about stock,
not about Ihwachae?

00:07:04.760 --> 00:07:05.760
Wait a minute.

00:07:06.260 --> 00:07:07.700
But why equal shares?

00:07:08.570 --> 00:07:11.040
Do you intend to make
the two boys compete?

00:07:11.170 --> 00:07:14.140
Exactly.
Once the shares are transferred,

00:07:14.410 --> 00:07:17.340
I'll throw my full support
behind the one who performs better.

00:07:18.610 --> 00:07:20.510
No, wait a second.

00:07:21.180 --> 00:07:24.680
For 20 years, you've been pitting me
against that witch,

00:07:24.680 --> 00:07:27.120
and now you're going to put Hyun Jun
through the same thing?

00:07:27.850 --> 00:07:30.720
This is about
who will be Adele Group's successor.

00:07:31.660 --> 00:07:34.290
I obviously need to see
which of them is more competent.

00:07:34.490 --> 00:07:35.490
Also,

00:07:37.460 --> 00:07:40.870
their marriages will factor
into my evaluation.

00:07:42.530 --> 00:07:44.140
I'll be watching closely to see...

00:07:44.140 --> 00:07:46.570
whether they can
pull off a marriage...

00:07:46.870 --> 00:07:49.010
with the partner I choose,
when I say.

00:07:50.610 --> 00:07:53.080
If by some off chance...

00:07:53.980 --> 00:07:55.810
you try any funny business
behind my back,

00:07:58.920 --> 00:08:01.750
whoever it is
will pay a steep price.

00:08:02.590 --> 00:08:04.890
So none of you cause any trouble.

00:08:05.620 --> 00:08:08.990
Stop going around
stirring up useless trouble,

00:08:09.630 --> 00:08:12.330
and stay away
from places like Ihwachae.

00:08:13.330 --> 00:08:15.530
Still, this is unreasonable.

00:08:15.530 --> 00:08:17.740
Do you want me to cut
Hyun Jun's shares in half?

00:08:18.470 --> 00:08:22.040
- Honey.
- We're done here, so leave.

00:08:23.070 --> 00:08:24.080
Leave.

00:08:37.960 --> 00:08:41.690
What is it?
Do you have something else to say?

00:08:43.830 --> 00:08:47.300
Regarding Dr. Baek
and Min Jun studying abroad,

00:08:47.830 --> 00:08:50.270
I need to find out if he's onto me.

00:08:52.370 --> 00:08:53.540
It looked like...

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:56.340
you had something more to say to me.

00:08:57.040 --> 00:08:58.040
Or am I wrong?

00:09:12.960 --> 00:09:14.460
So, why the family meeting?

00:09:14.930 --> 00:09:18.730
What was so important
that I was excluded?

00:09:18.830 --> 00:09:21.000
Competition? An evaluation?

00:09:21.170 --> 00:09:24.070
What is there to test
when there's already a clear successor?

00:09:24.140 --> 00:09:27.100
What? He's making Hyun Jun compete?

00:09:27.200 --> 00:09:30.610
I've put up with him for 20 years
and made him rich. Isn't it enough?

00:09:30.810 --> 00:09:33.080
Now he wants to control Hyun Jun
however he likes?

00:09:33.140 --> 00:09:36.950
What? He's going to put Hyun Jun
through the wringer?

00:09:37.580 --> 00:09:38.720
Are you crazy?

00:09:38.980 --> 00:09:41.850
I have enough on my mind
without you acting like an idiot!

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:43.990
Just shut it and get lost.

00:09:46.220 --> 00:09:47.330
Ms. Oh.

00:09:47.630 --> 00:09:51.360
- Why are you taking it out on him?
- Hyun Jun...

00:09:58.870 --> 00:10:01.740
The dictator of this household,
as always.

00:10:03.170 --> 00:10:06.810
Chairman Park does
whatever he wants, as usual.

00:10:07.950 --> 00:10:10.410
My "my way or the highway" attitude.

00:10:10.820 --> 00:10:12.620
Didn't you say
I got it all from Dad?

00:10:12.850 --> 00:10:16.250
Right. No matter what anyone says,
you are Park Tae Ho's son.

00:10:21.530 --> 00:10:24.760
So do exactly as your father says.
No questions asked.

00:10:24.900 --> 00:10:25.900
And do it perfectly.

00:10:26.800 --> 00:10:30.000
You can't ever lose to that punk,
Park Min Jun. Understand?

00:10:30.070 --> 00:10:32.640
One minute ago, you were furious
about him having to compete.

00:10:33.770 --> 00:10:35.810
I told you to butt out!

00:10:35.940 --> 00:10:39.240
Ms. Oh, come on.
You'll pass out if you keep yelling.

00:10:39.310 --> 00:10:42.550
I'll get out of your hair,
so just calm down. Okay?

00:10:43.150 --> 00:10:45.180
- But...
- Okay. Relax.

00:10:45.250 --> 00:10:48.690
Hey, Hyun Jun. Park Hyun Jun!

00:10:53.290 --> 00:10:55.460
I was just worried...

00:10:56.030 --> 00:10:58.130
he'd make things really hard...

00:10:58.700 --> 00:11:00.900
for our Hyun Jun.

00:11:00.970 --> 00:11:04.200
If you're so worried,
start by fixing the way you talk.

00:11:05.800 --> 00:11:08.010
Who do you think you are,
calling him "our Hyun Jun?"

00:11:10.470 --> 00:11:12.140
Get your act together...

00:11:12.580 --> 00:11:14.550
so you don't ruin
Hyun Jun's reputation. Got it?

00:11:30.130 --> 00:11:31.130
Myung Hui.

00:11:33.200 --> 00:11:34.570
Don't take it too far.

00:11:38.640 --> 00:11:41.170
Just as you are an asset
to the company,

00:11:41.440 --> 00:11:44.610
my wife is useful in her own way.

00:11:45.810 --> 00:11:47.580
Don't try to one-up my wife...

00:11:48.080 --> 00:11:50.610
by going to places like Ihwachae.

00:11:50.980 --> 00:11:52.920
Don't leave
any video evidence behind,

00:11:53.650 --> 00:11:55.550
like you did in the wardrobe room.

00:11:57.190 --> 00:11:58.190
Just as I thought.

00:11:58.660 --> 00:12:01.190
You really do know everything,
Chairman Park.

00:12:02.630 --> 00:12:05.260
This is my company
and my family we're talking about.

00:12:05.630 --> 00:12:07.300
Of course I know what's going on.

00:12:08.430 --> 00:12:12.170
I can turn a blind eye
to the wardrobe room and Ihwachae,

00:12:13.440 --> 00:12:15.740
but if you stir up trouble again,

00:12:17.110 --> 00:12:18.510
you'll be in for a world of hurt.

00:12:22.480 --> 00:12:24.950
He still doesn't know
about Dr. Baek...

00:12:25.020 --> 00:12:26.450
or Min Jun studying abroad.

00:12:27.050 --> 00:12:28.050
That's right.

00:12:28.350 --> 00:12:31.520
If you knew,
you wouldn't be this calm.

00:12:32.390 --> 00:12:33.520
Myung Hui.

00:12:36.660 --> 00:12:38.230
Ever since you lost your memory,

00:12:40.200 --> 00:12:41.570
you've become a different person.

00:12:46.040 --> 00:12:50.440
When we first met,
you had no talent for business,

00:12:50.710 --> 00:12:54.480
and you certainly weren't the type
to scheme against my wife.

00:12:56.310 --> 00:12:57.650
Sometimes when I look at you,

00:12:58.920 --> 00:13:00.890
it's less like
you lost your memory...

00:13:00.890 --> 00:13:03.620
and more like you're someone else.

00:13:13.060 --> 00:13:15.970
Yes. I am a completely different person.

00:13:17.170 --> 00:13:19.840
I came back from the brink of death.

00:13:20.040 --> 00:13:21.670
That would change anyone.

00:13:22.940 --> 00:13:24.440
In place of my lost memories,

00:13:24.810 --> 00:13:26.840
a new sense of purpose took root.

00:13:30.010 --> 00:13:31.020
I see.

00:13:32.680 --> 00:13:35.220
That sense of purpose...

00:13:35.820 --> 00:13:40.860
protected my son and Adele,
so I can't say it's all bad.

00:13:41.430 --> 00:13:42.430
However,

00:13:44.530 --> 00:13:46.600
only go as far as I'll allow.

00:13:47.430 --> 00:13:49.330
That's the only way I can...

00:13:50.100 --> 00:13:52.040
look after you and Min Jun.

00:13:55.170 --> 00:13:58.840
I'll be the one to neatly take care
of all the messy...

00:14:00.340 --> 00:14:02.050
and complicated problems.

00:14:23.500 --> 00:14:25.540
Why does Baek Jin Ju get everything?

00:14:26.000 --> 00:14:28.270
She gets both Min Jun and Adele.

00:14:28.710 --> 00:14:30.510
And now she gets a say
in my dad's position?

00:14:31.840 --> 00:14:33.810
What am I supposed to do now?

00:14:34.910 --> 00:14:36.950
My goodness,
what is all that racket?

00:14:37.350 --> 00:14:38.850
Gosh, what happened in here?

00:14:39.720 --> 00:14:42.750
Goodness me.
Just look at the state of this desk.

00:14:43.120 --> 00:14:44.490
You foolish girl.

00:14:45.120 --> 00:14:47.320
I just knew this would happen.

00:14:47.630 --> 00:14:50.960
You got jealous for no good reason
and hurt Jin Ju's feelings.

00:14:51.030 --> 00:14:54.730
That's why Jin Ju ran to her dad
without a word.

00:14:56.100 --> 00:14:59.170
Goodness, it was the same
the day CEO Baek visited.

00:14:59.240 --> 00:15:01.740
You ran around like a lunatic.

00:15:01.840 --> 00:15:04.210
Goodness, you wretched girl.

00:15:04.340 --> 00:15:07.910
Throwing a tantrum
only hurts you in the end.

00:15:08.210 --> 00:15:11.250
If you had just been patient
until Jin Ju left for the UK,

00:15:11.380 --> 00:15:13.050
do you think CEO Baek
would've just stood by?

00:15:13.120 --> 00:15:17.020
He would've thanked us
with a hefty sum of money.

00:15:17.020 --> 00:15:19.420
But no, you just had to ruin it all!

00:15:19.490 --> 00:15:22.090
Get out. Get out right now!

00:15:22.430 --> 00:15:26.100
Don't you dare raise your voice at me,
you ungrateful brat.

00:15:26.700 --> 00:15:28.830
- Goodness.
- You're just like Dad.

00:15:29.700 --> 00:15:32.270
Always bowing and scraping,
mooching off of people.

00:15:32.540 --> 00:15:33.900
It's so humiliating.

00:15:34.310 --> 00:15:36.040
It's pathetic!

00:15:36.840 --> 00:15:39.880
What was that, you brat?
Let go of me.

00:15:40.040 --> 00:15:43.210
My gosh. How dare you?

00:15:43.550 --> 00:15:46.420
Choi Yu Na, open this door now!
Do you hear me?

00:15:47.180 --> 00:15:49.290
I said open up!

00:15:49.620 --> 00:15:51.860
Why you little...

00:15:52.190 --> 00:15:53.290
For goodness' sake.

00:15:53.560 --> 00:15:56.490
Darn it. For crying out loud.

00:15:56.490 --> 00:15:58.230
Have you lost your mind?

00:16:24.420 --> 00:16:26.990
There's no need to be so nervous.

00:16:29.690 --> 00:16:33.130
I called you here
because I have a proposal for you.

00:16:43.540 --> 00:16:46.480
You're going to help me
and my father?

00:16:48.210 --> 00:16:49.780
There's one condition, of course.

00:16:50.810 --> 00:16:52.980
You have to do exactly as I say,

00:16:54.390 --> 00:16:55.490
without any mistakes.

00:16:57.890 --> 00:17:00.390
What is it you want me to do?

00:17:01.390 --> 00:17:02.430
That...

00:17:03.690 --> 00:17:06.200
I'll tell you
after you promise to do it.

00:17:11.940 --> 00:17:14.170
I don't think you're in a position
to hesitate.

00:17:15.210 --> 00:17:18.410
CEO Choi Sam Sik will soon be forced
out of the company,

00:17:19.080 --> 00:17:22.710
and then you, Ms. Yu Na,
will have your wings clipped...

00:17:22.880 --> 00:17:24.250
before you even get
the chance to fly.

00:17:25.020 --> 00:17:27.890
You'll be too busy worrying
about putting food on the table.

00:17:31.790 --> 00:17:32.790
Meanwhile,

00:17:33.720 --> 00:17:35.960
what do you think will happen
to CEO Baek's daughter?

00:17:38.130 --> 00:17:41.770
She'll become
a top jewelry designer and soar.

00:17:42.200 --> 00:17:45.870
She'll fly so high
she'll stand right beside Min Jun.

00:17:47.440 --> 00:17:49.570
You will be at the bottom,

00:17:49.940 --> 00:17:51.740
while Baek Jin Ju will be
at the very top.

00:17:52.580 --> 00:17:55.480
The two of you will be living
in completely different worlds.

00:17:57.380 --> 00:17:58.420
In different...

00:17:59.280 --> 00:18:00.280
worlds?

00:18:02.520 --> 00:18:05.060
Whether you accept
my proposal or not,

00:18:05.960 --> 00:18:07.660
your decision...

00:18:08.390 --> 00:18:11.090
could change both your future...

00:18:12.760 --> 00:18:14.130
and Baek Jin Ju's.

00:18:40.220 --> 00:18:42.590
(Adele Group New Design Competition)

00:18:44.560 --> 00:18:47.130
I've chosen this
as this year's Grand Prize winner.

00:18:54.810 --> 00:18:58.210
The preliminary round design
was nothing special,

00:18:58.580 --> 00:19:01.910
but this design for the finals
was incredibly fresh.

00:19:03.150 --> 00:19:05.620
Doesn't winning the Grand Prize
mean you'll get to study abroad...

00:19:06.050 --> 00:19:07.920
with Adele's support?

00:19:09.090 --> 00:19:10.220
A chance to study abroad?

00:19:13.820 --> 00:19:18.430
If you accept my proposal,
you'll be given even bigger wings.

00:19:19.660 --> 00:19:21.730
And if you work hard
and keep soaring...

00:19:22.800 --> 00:19:24.840
Who knows? You might even end up...

00:19:25.370 --> 00:19:26.700
right by Min Jun's side.

00:19:46.490 --> 00:19:47.760
Soaring higher?

00:19:49.290 --> 00:19:50.830
To where Park Min Jun is?

00:19:52.730 --> 00:19:55.170
All the way to the top of Adele?

00:19:57.700 --> 00:19:59.040
Not Baek Jin Ju,

00:20:01.070 --> 00:20:02.070
but me?

00:20:22.690 --> 00:20:24.560
Looks like she took the bait.

00:20:25.700 --> 00:20:26.800
Now, put the pressure on.

00:20:27.630 --> 00:20:29.970
Once she's cornered,
she'll make a quick decision.

00:20:30.570 --> 00:20:31.570
Yes, sir.

00:20:35.640 --> 00:20:38.040
I told you,
I'll make it for you myself.

00:20:38.210 --> 00:20:40.340
But Dad, you're so busy.

00:20:40.540 --> 00:20:41.750
You're taking calls left and right,

00:20:41.750 --> 00:20:43.550
checking emails,
and having video conferences.

00:20:44.150 --> 00:20:45.720
Aren't you staying
just for my sake...

00:20:45.720 --> 00:20:46.920
when you should be going back?

00:20:46.980 --> 00:20:50.920
No, not at all.
I still have some business here.

00:20:52.220 --> 00:20:54.360
There's actually something
I need your help with.

00:20:54.790 --> 00:20:55.790
My help?

00:20:58.300 --> 00:21:00.660
You still have
the P.O. box key, right?

00:21:01.260 --> 00:21:03.930
Of course. I always have it with me.

00:21:04.700 --> 00:21:07.900
Good. In a few days,
an important item...

00:21:09.010 --> 00:21:11.540
(New Message)

00:21:14.440 --> 00:21:16.980
The item you mentioned
has been sent.

00:21:22.020 --> 00:21:23.290
(Interview with Park Tae Ho,
Chairman of Adele Group)

00:21:25.860 --> 00:21:28.360
So that's Min Jun's father.

00:21:35.430 --> 00:21:36.800
Adele isn't a good choice.

00:21:37.700 --> 00:21:38.700
What?

00:21:38.840 --> 00:21:42.110
Don't think about working there,
even as a jewelry designer.

00:21:43.040 --> 00:21:46.940
It may be a famous corporation,
but it's not for you, Jin Ju.

00:21:48.410 --> 00:21:49.650
It could be...

00:21:50.410 --> 00:21:51.820
more dangerous than you think.

00:21:52.820 --> 00:21:54.480
Adele is dangerous?

00:21:58.190 --> 00:22:00.720
I have to take this call.
You finish up.

00:22:06.060 --> 00:22:08.130
Did he say Adele was dangerous?

00:22:09.600 --> 00:22:11.370
Is he talking
about Min Jun's father?

00:22:14.670 --> 00:22:17.110
(Interview with Park Tae Ho,
Chairman of Adele Group)

00:22:23.750 --> 00:22:24.780
What's that?

00:22:30.120 --> 00:22:32.120
(Adele Group New Design Competition)

00:22:34.760 --> 00:22:35.760
(Adele Group
New Design Competition Results)

00:22:35.830 --> 00:22:37.790
(Grand Prize Winner: Choi Yu Na)

00:22:50.310 --> 00:22:52.380
Choi Yu Na, seriously?

00:22:53.140 --> 00:22:55.680
Did you steal Jin Ju's design
and enter it in the competition?

00:22:58.050 --> 00:22:59.180
Steal it?

00:22:59.880 --> 00:23:01.650
How can you just accuse me
out of the blue?

00:23:01.920 --> 00:23:04.420
We both know that's Jin Ju's design.

00:23:13.030 --> 00:23:14.600
(Grand Prize Winner: Choi Yu Na)

00:23:22.210 --> 00:23:23.470
What about it?

00:23:24.170 --> 00:23:27.610
Don't call me a thief
unless you have proof.

00:23:31.980 --> 00:23:36.120
Do you have proof it's her design,
or that I stole it?

00:23:45.460 --> 00:23:48.000
Jin Ju designed this
for me personally.

00:23:48.870 --> 00:23:50.630
Do I really need any more proof?

00:23:53.600 --> 00:23:56.170
Go to Adele
and confess you stole it.

00:23:57.410 --> 00:23:58.410
What?

00:23:58.880 --> 00:24:01.610
I read that the grand prize winner
gets to study abroad.

00:24:01.950 --> 00:24:04.110
It wouldn't be right to win that
with a stolen design.

00:24:11.120 --> 00:24:12.920
Let me study in the UK too.

00:24:13.220 --> 00:24:15.560
Dad, why are you always
comparing me to her?

00:24:15.890 --> 00:24:18.230
But you can't even give me
the one thing I ask for.

00:24:18.430 --> 00:24:19.760
How am I the only disappointment
in this house?

00:24:20.760 --> 00:24:23.300
Why do you always put me down? Why?

00:24:26.200 --> 00:24:27.200
Stop it.

00:24:27.770 --> 00:24:29.610
It's Yu Na's design.

00:24:33.710 --> 00:24:35.910
We came up
with a lot of similar designs...

00:24:35.910 --> 00:24:37.480
when we were in the US together.

00:24:38.050 --> 00:24:39.950
That must've happened again.

00:24:42.320 --> 00:24:44.090
Jin Ju, hold on.

00:24:45.420 --> 00:24:46.890
Congratulations, Yu Na.

00:25:04.610 --> 00:25:05.640
Congratulations?

00:25:08.850 --> 00:25:09.850
She's congratulating me?

00:25:18.220 --> 00:25:21.120
A similar design?
Why would you lie like that?

00:25:21.690 --> 00:25:23.890
Everyone makes mistakes.

00:25:24.190 --> 00:25:26.130
She's my friend.
Can't I cover for her this one time?

00:25:26.130 --> 00:25:28.430
As her friend, you should
help her make things right.

00:25:28.970 --> 00:25:30.530
Right now,
it's just one stolen design,

00:25:30.530 --> 00:25:32.840
but if you let this slide,
she could steal something bigger.

00:25:33.740 --> 00:25:35.510
I'm sure Yu Na regrets it.

00:25:35.770 --> 00:25:38.610
She was desperate
for this chance to study abroad...

00:25:38.610 --> 00:25:40.240
and must've acted without thinking.

00:25:41.440 --> 00:25:44.410
I feel like I've been causing Yu Na
a lot of stress,

00:25:45.550 --> 00:25:47.450
so I want to make it up to her,
at least this way.

00:25:48.490 --> 00:25:51.390
Can we just let this go?
For my sake, please?

00:25:51.760 --> 00:25:53.860
If I'm okay with it,
that should be enough.

00:25:56.830 --> 00:25:58.190
So it only matters
if you're okay with it?

00:25:58.760 --> 00:26:00.730
That design means a lot to me, too.

00:26:01.100 --> 00:26:03.300
It was a promise we made,
a memory we shared.

00:26:04.600 --> 00:26:06.340
You may have had your design stolen,

00:26:06.700 --> 00:26:09.070
but I feel like I've been robbed
of a precious memory.

00:26:10.840 --> 00:26:11.910
Then...

00:26:12.740 --> 00:26:13.810
let's just make a new one.

00:26:14.580 --> 00:26:17.180
We can always make a new one,
one that's even more amazing.

00:26:17.750 --> 00:26:19.950
Right? Please?

00:26:25.620 --> 00:26:26.720
Min Jun.

00:26:27.990 --> 00:26:28.990
Min Jun!

00:26:31.700 --> 00:26:32.700
Min Jun.

00:26:36.200 --> 00:26:37.200
Make it up to me?

00:26:38.600 --> 00:26:39.900
Let me study abroad?

00:26:43.010 --> 00:26:45.740
You can come up
with a design like that so easily?

00:26:48.780 --> 00:26:50.210
You're still pitying me?

00:26:52.650 --> 00:26:54.120
Are you really
humiliating me like this?

00:27:02.530 --> 00:27:05.430
(Adele Group)

00:27:14.100 --> 00:27:15.770
Chairman Park really is a scary man.

00:27:16.640 --> 00:27:18.540
The wardrobe room incident
and the thing with Ihwachae...

00:27:19.310 --> 00:27:21.310
It means he's been watching
our every move.

00:27:22.780 --> 00:27:25.320
We'll have to be extra careful
when we get Dr. Baek's evidence.

00:27:28.120 --> 00:27:30.320
You have a plan
to get him off our tail, right?

00:27:31.020 --> 00:27:32.820
Double-check everything
so there are no errors.

00:27:34.460 --> 00:27:37.390
What Chairman Park said
is really bothering me.

00:27:38.190 --> 00:27:40.360
Okay, I got it. Don't worry.

00:27:41.500 --> 00:27:43.470
But Min Jun studying abroad
is going to be a problem.

00:27:44.300 --> 00:27:46.470
At this rate,
Chairman Park is going to find out.

00:27:49.610 --> 00:27:50.910
When the evidence arrives,

00:27:51.880 --> 00:27:53.740
I'll have to tell Min Jun first.

00:27:55.080 --> 00:27:56.080
About what happened to Myung Hui?

00:27:57.050 --> 00:27:59.750
But you've hidden it for so long
because you were afraid to hurt him.

00:27:59.980 --> 00:28:03.020
If Chairman Park finds out
Min Jun is going abroad, he'll act.

00:28:04.120 --> 00:28:05.390
I have no choice...

00:28:06.120 --> 00:28:08.060
if I want Min Jun to give up
before Chairman Park finds out.

00:28:09.790 --> 00:28:12.000
I have to change his mind,
even if it means...

00:28:12.100 --> 00:28:13.200
telling him how his mother died.

00:28:14.530 --> 00:28:15.530
You're right.

00:28:16.030 --> 00:28:17.870
He's going to find out anyway...

00:28:18.370 --> 00:28:19.670
once the evidence is made public.

00:28:21.500 --> 00:28:23.270
Just as Min Jun will have
to come to terms...

00:28:23.270 --> 00:28:24.440
with his birth mother's death,

00:28:26.340 --> 00:28:28.450
I'll bear his resentment toward me.

00:28:37.090 --> 00:28:38.090
It's Dr. Baek.

00:28:38.690 --> 00:28:40.060
I bet the evidence has arrived.

00:28:45.660 --> 00:28:49.230
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

00:28:52.600 --> 00:28:54.340
This is Choi Yu Na.

00:28:56.340 --> 00:28:57.810
I'm willing to do whatever you ask,

00:28:59.040 --> 00:29:00.040
Chairman Park.

00:29:01.980 --> 00:29:04.680
Yes. I'll do anything you ask.

00:29:08.250 --> 00:29:11.020
(Adele Group)

00:29:15.630 --> 00:29:16.630
Yes, Dr. Baek.

00:29:17.860 --> 00:29:19.430
I'll be there, no matter what.

00:29:21.030 --> 00:29:22.430
I'll be there to collect
the evidence my sister left behind.

00:29:23.870 --> 00:29:25.870
The bloody pearl she had
in her hand.

00:29:55.060 --> 00:29:58.130
(Pearl in Red)

00:29:58.430 --> 00:30:01.240
We'll get the evidence
my sister left behind, right?

00:30:01.240 --> 00:30:03.140
There's no way
I'm letting them take it this time.

00:30:03.140 --> 00:30:04.140
Ma'am!

00:30:04.710 --> 00:30:08.080
Jin Ju, after looking down on me
and acting all innocent,

00:30:08.080 --> 00:30:09.450
you're stabbing me in the back?

00:30:09.580 --> 00:30:11.280
It'll just be
a minor car accident, right?

00:30:11.350 --> 00:30:13.980
What, are you afraid I'll kill them?

00:30:13.980 --> 00:30:16.220
Just think of it
as a minor accident...

00:30:16.250 --> 00:30:17.850
and brush it off.

00:30:17.920 --> 00:30:20.790
Right. He said
it'd just be a minor accident.

00:30:21.090 --> 00:30:22.690
- Dad!
- But...

00:30:23.460 --> 00:30:24.930
what if it's not?

00:30:25.600 --> 00:30:27.600
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)